last_episode_to_air.name: In the Name of Love and Justice
last_episode_to_air.overview: With Nam-soon on the brink of death — Hee-sik rushes to find an antidote. Nam-soon faces Si-o once again, but witnesses a surprising turn.

name: Strong Girl Nam-soon
overview: Gifted with superhuman strength, a young woman returns to Korea to find her birth family — only to be entangled in a drug case that could test her power.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Spin-off of k-drama/series Strong Girl Do Bong-soon. It's story of a daughter, mother, and grandmother with superhuman strength who get entangled in a drug case. Same as its original series that make pun from the lead character Do Bong-soon who is from Dobong district, now the story of Gang Nam-soon is around Gangnam district.

tagline: We are here to beat up the weaklings!

episodes.name: Birth of the Strong Girl
episodes.overview: Desperate for a reunion, Hwang Geum-ju seemingly finds her long-lost daughter. After discovering the truth, Gang Nam-soon prepares for her trip to Korea.

episodes.name: Gangnam, Here I Come
episodes.overview: Nam-soon begins her search for her parents in Korea but experiences some roadblocks. Geum-ju suspects something's off with her newfound daughter.

episodes.name: Three Generations
episodes.overview: The incident at the Han River puts a spotlight on Nam-soon. As Kang Hee-sik spends more time with Nam-soon, he connects the dots about her family.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: After a dramatic reunion, Nam-soon becomes closer to her family. As Hee-sik continues to investigate a drug case, Nam-soon lends her assistance.

episodes.name: Vigilante of Seoul
episodes.overview: As Nam-soon assists Hee-sik in his drug investigation, she has a run-in with the ominous Ryu Si-o. Ri Hwa-ja plots her revenge against Nam-soon.

episodes.name: Mystery X
episodes.overview: Hee-sik witnesses the jarring effects of the drug when it strikes his team leader. Nam-soon's search for evidence garners attention from foes.

episodes.name: Moonbow
episodes.overview: Geum-ju pays a strategic visit to Si-o, who has his own motives. During a birthday dinner, Nam-soon's family questions her growing kinship with Hee-sik.

episodes.name: Light and Shadow of Gangnam
episodes.overview: Hee-sik begins to worry about Nam-soon after Si-o promotes her into his inner circle. Geum-ju probes deeper into a suspicious businessman.

episodes.name: The Root of Vice
episodes.overview: Nam-soon pulls off a bold heist, putting Si-o on high alert. During a tense meeting, Geum-ju challenges Si-o — who in return begins plotting his revenge.

episodes.name: The Stand-ins
episodes.overview: Geum-ju falls victim to Si-o's attack, but proves she's one step ahead of him. As Nam-soon finally tracks down the drugs, her brother succumbs to them.

episodes.name: Breaking Point
episodes.overview: The drug infiltrates Nam-soon's family — prompting a search of the source and an antidote. A mourning Hee-sik furiously goes after Si-o's inner circle.

episodes.name: Diamond Cuts Diamond
episodes.overview: Si-o learns of Geum-ju's ruse and decides to expand his target. As the drug case becomes more intense, Hee-sik asks Nam-soon to move in with him.

episodes.name: Save the Sea Hares
episodes.overview: To find out Nam-soon's identity, Si-o narrows down his search and goes after her family. Hee-sik faces harsh discipline after news of the drug goes wide.

episodes.name: Forewarned Bloodbath
episodes.overview: Si-o vows revenge after discovering the truth about Nam-soon. While Hee-sik continues his investigation, Nam-soon and her family go on a trip to Busan.

episodes.name: Strong Girl Nam-soon
episodes.overview: Mourning the loss of Hwa-ja, Nam-soon directly challenges Si-o. But he refuses to lose, forcing her to endure incredible pain to save her adopted mother.

episodes.name: In the Name of Love and Justice
episodes.overview: With Nam-soon on the brink of death — Hee-sik rushes to find an antidote. Nam-soon faces Si-o once again, but witnesses a surprising turn.
